preference.name: CATIA_savemanager_unmodifiable_attr_list
preference.preference_description: ItemRev.item_revision_id This preference defines an attribute list. These attributes will not be modified in the SaveManager. The attribute list must adhere to the naming format "keyword.attributename". List of keywords: - For item's attribute = Item. - For item revision's attribute = ItemRev. - For item master form's attribute = ItemMaster. - For item revision master form's attribute = ItemRevMaster. - For dataset's attribute = Dst. The attributename should be the attribute real name. For example: Item.item_id; ItemRev.item_revision_id; Dst.pubr_object_id; Dst.object_name
